Bandwidth (or spectral) efficiency of M-PSK modulation schemes increases with increasing of modulation order M (unlike, for example, M-FSK):Haykin, S., 2001. Communication Systems, John Wiley&Sons. Inc. - p. 368

\rho = \frac{\log_2M}{2} \quad [(\text{bits}/\text{s}) / \text{Hz}]

